Make sure the following packages from the Standard Repositories are installed:

sfml sfml-dev libsfml-dev libsfml-doc libsqlite3-0 libsqlite3-dev

Add the following repository:

ppa:texus/tgui-0.8

And then install the following additional package:

libtgui-dev

The additional following third-party libraries are needed to compile:

- simpleini https://github.com/brofield/simpleini/
- jsoncpp https://github.com/open-source-parsers/jsoncpp
- sqlite_modern_cpp https://github.com/SqliteModernCpp/sqlite_modern_cpp

